@host = http://localhost:5038
@apiKey = reminder-hemlig-123

### Skapa en påminnelse
POST {{host}}/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "userId": "1",
  "loanId": "1",
  "itemId": 1,
  "itemTitle": "Testbok",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-01T00:00:00Z",
  "isSent": false
}

### Hämta alla påminnelser
GET {{host}}/api/reminders
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Räkna försenade
GET {{host}}/api/reminders/overdue/count
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Skapa en bevakning
POST {{host}}/api/watches
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "itemId": 7,
  "itemTitle": "Att leda i offentlig sektor",
  "isActive": true
}

### Hämta alla bevakningar
GET {{host}}/api/watches
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Hämta bevakningar för användare 1
GET {{host}}/api/watches?userId=1
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Test 1: Skapa bevakning
POST {{host}}/api/watches
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "itemId": 5,
  "itemTitle": "Clean Code",
  "isActive": true
}
### Test 2: Hämta alla bevakningar
GET {{host}}/api/watches
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
### Test 3: Skapa påminnelse
POST {{host}}/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "loanId": 10,
  "itemId": 5,
  "itemTitle": "Clean Code",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-08T00:00:00Z",
  "isSent": false,
  "watchId": 2
}
### Test 4: Hämta försenade påminnelser
GET {{host}}/api/reminders?overdue=true
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
### Test 5: Räkna försenade
GET {{host}}/api/reminders/overdue/count
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
### Test 6: Markera påminnelse som skickad
PUT {{host}}/api/reminders/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "isSent": true,
  "dueDate": "2026-03-08T00:00:00Z",
  "itemTitle": "Clean Code"
}
### Test 7: Ta bort bevakning
DELETE {{host}}/api/watches/2
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
### Test 8: Ta bort påminnelse
DELETE {{host}}/api/reminders/1
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
### Test Azure: Räkna försenade (live)
GET https://app-sos100-reminder-service.azurewebsites.net/api/reminders/overdue/count
X-Api-Key: reminder-hemlig-123